ure\", \"from\": 17528, \"to\": 17555}, {\"ngram\": \"a clergy\", \"from\": 17579, \"to\": 17587}, {\"ngram\": \"the standard\", \"from\": 17607, \"to\": 17619}, {\"ngram\": \"a decaying secularity\", \"from\": 17623, \"to\": 17644}, {\"ngram\": \"the Standard\", \"from\": 17657, \"to\": 17669}, {\"ngram\": \"Christ\", \"from\": 17673, \"to\": 17679}, {\"ngram\": \"the King\", \"from\": 17680, \"to\": 17688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not believe me?\", \"from\": 17690, \"to\": 17708, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Look at their seminaries-turned-ghost-towns, testament to aggiornamento gone awry.\", \"from\": 17709, \"to\": 17791, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their seminaries\", \"from\": 17717, \"to\": 17733}, {\"ngram\": \"-turned-ghost-towns\", \"from\": 17733, \"to\": 17752}, {\"ngram\": \"testament\", \"from\": 17754, \"to\": 17763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A recent Order of nuns called a festive dinner to celebrate the announcement of their demise.Yes, you say, but wasn't there the American bishop who registered a gentle reservation?\", \"from\": 17792, \"to\": 17972, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17920, \"end\": 17928, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999730244989471, \"rank\": 2.4748056521449384e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A recent Order\", \"from\": 17792, \"to\": 17806}, {\"ngram\": \"nuns\", \"from\": 17810, \"to\": 17814}, {\"ngram\": \"a festive dinner\", \"from\": 17822, \"to\": 17838}, {\"ngram\": \"the announcement\", \"from\": 17852, \"to\": 17868}, {\"ngram\": \"their demise\", \"from\": 17872, \"to\": 17884}, {\"ngram\": \"a gentle reservation\", \"from\": 17951, \"to\": 17971}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, true enough.\", \"from\": 17973, \"to\": 17990, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sente