ion\", \"from\": 28446, \"to\": 28463}, {\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 28468, \"to\": 28475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now that barbarian was at the very gates of Rome.\", \"from\": 28477, \"to\": 28526, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 28521, \"end\": 28525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope\", \"score\": 0.8768054666094818, \"rank\": 0.0603414769626484, \"text\": \"Rome\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pope\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"barbarian\", \"from\": 28486, \"to\": 28495}, {\"ngram\": \"the very gates\", \"from\": 28503, \"to\": 28517}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All seemed to be lost.\", \"from\": 28527, \"to\": 28549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pope Leo the Great, in solemn procession with priests, deacons, and acolytes swinging golden thuribles, went out to meet the bloodthirsty chieftain.\", \"from\": 28550, \"to\": 28698, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Great\", \"from\": 28559, \"to\": 28568}, {\"ngram\": \"solemn procession\", \"from\": 28573, \"to\": 28590}, {\"ngram\": \"priests\", \"from\": 28596, \"to\": 28603}, {\"ngram\": \"deacons\", \"from\": 28605, \"to\": 28612}, {\"ngram\": \"golden thuribles\", \"from\": 28636, \"to\": 28652}, {\"ngram\": \"the bloodthirsty chieftain\", \"from\": 28671, \"to\": 28697}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Face-to-face, they spoke.\", \"from\": 28699, \"to\": 28724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"face\", \"from\": 28707, \"to\": 28711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a brief conversation, Attila turned around and commanded his troops to retreat.\", \"from\": 28725, \"to\": 28810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 28753, \"end\": 28759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Attila\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1629106735478176e-15, \"text\": \"Attila\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Attila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http:/