": 29611, \"to\": 29618}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 29634, \"to\": 29643}, {\"ngram\": \"The blood-dimmed tide\", \"from\": 29644, \"to\": 29665}, {\"ngram\": \"everywhereThe ceremony\", \"from\": 29681, \"to\": 29703}, {\"ngram\": \"innocence\", \"from\": 29707, \"to\": 29716}, {\"ngram\": \"drowned;The best lack\", \"from\": 29720, \"to\": 29741}, {\"ngram\": \"passionate intensity\", \"from\": 29785, \"to\": 29805}, {\"ngram\": \"The tragedy\", \"from\": 29806, \"to\": 29817}, {\"ngram\": \"the outrageous blasphemy\", \"from\": 29826, \"to\": 29850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the absence of howling outrage.\", \"from\": 29852, \"to\": 29890, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the absence\", \"from\": 29859, \"to\": 29870}, {\"ngram\": \"outrage\", \"from\": 29882, \"to\": 29889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No such supine reaction would have met such an attack on Islam.\", \"from\": 29891, \"to\": 29954, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No such supine reaction\", \"from\": 29891, \"to\": 29914}, {\"ngram\": \"such an attack\", \"from\": 29930, \"to\": 29944}, {\"ngram\": \"Islam\", \"from\": 29948, \"to\": 29953}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For all its wild aberrations, it does not lack the manliness of instantaneous fury.\", \"from\": 29955, \"to\": 30038, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all its wild aberrations\", \"from\": 29959, \"to\": 29983}, {\"ngram\": \"the manliness\", \"from\": 30002, \"to\": 30015}, {\"ngram\": \"instantaneous fury\", \"from\": 30019, \"to\": 30037}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not so the once chest-thumping Catholicism of the saints and martyrs.\", \"from\": 30039, \"to\": 30108, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Not so the once chest-thumping Catholicism\", \"from\": 30039, \"to\": 30081}, {\"ngram\": \"the saints\", \"from\": 30085, \"to\": 30095}, {\"ngram\": \"martyrs\", \"from\": 30100, \"to\": 30107}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sixty years ago, that millennial Catholic trademark was thought embarrassing for a Church in a hurry to make friends with the world.\", \"from\": 30109, \"to\": 30241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 30142, \"end\": 30150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999999942048134, \"rank\": 5.170043206974671e-09, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a Church\", \"from\": 30190, \"to\": 30198}, {\"ngram\": \"a hurry\", \"from\": 30202, \"to\": 30209}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 30218, \"to\": 30225}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 30231, \"to\": 30240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Historic Catholic boasts such as the Crusades, the vanquishing of the Old Pagan gods, and the conversion of the nations have been quietly shelved for a more user-friendly Catholicism.\", \"from\": 30242, \"to\": 30425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 30251, \"end\": 30259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999999942048134, \"rank\": 5.170043206974671e-09, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Crusades\", \"from\": 30275, \"to\": 30287}, {\"ngram\": \"the vanquishing\", \"from\": 30289, \"to\": 30304}, {\"ngram\": \"the Old Pagan gods\", \"from\": 30308, \"to\": 30326}, {\"ngram\": \"the conversion\", \"from\": 30332, \"to\": 30346}, {\"ngram\": \"the nations\", \"from\": 30350, \"to\": 30361}, {\"ngram\": \"a more user-friendly Catholicism\", \"from\": 30392, \"to\": 30424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anathemas have been traded for something called \\\"dialogical listening\\\" and certitude by sensitivity to \\\"difference.\\\"\", \"from\": 30426, \"to\": 30542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Anathemas\", \"from\": 30426, \"to\": 30435}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 30457, \"to\": 30466}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"dialogical listening\", \"from\": 30474, \"to\": 30495}, {\"ngram\": \"certitude\", \"from\": 30501, \"to\": 30510}, {\"ngram\": \"sensitivity\", \"from\": 30514, \"to\": 30525}, {\"ngram\": \"difference\", \"from\": 30530, \"to\": 30540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some members of the hierarchy have censured \\\"proselytism,\\\" a slur on bringing men to the Catholic Church.Catholics are now incessantly drilled on the one and only sin \\\"crying out to heaven for vengeance\\\": \\\"passing judgment.\\\"\", \"from\": 30543, \"to\": 30767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 30632, \"end\": 30640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999999942048134, \"rank\": 5.170043206974671e-09, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some members\", \"from\": 30543, \"to\": 30555}, {\"ngram\": \"the hierarchy\", \"from\": 30559, \"to\": 30572}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"proselytism\", \"from\": 30587, \"to\": 30599}, {\"ngram\": \"a slur\", \"from\": 30602, \"to\": 30608}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 30621, \"to\": 30624}, {\"ngram\": \"Catholics\", \"from\": 30648, \"to\": 30657}, {\"ngram\": \"the one and only sin\", \"from\": 30689, \"to\": 30709}, {\"ngram\": \"heaven\", \"from\": 30725, \"to\": 30731}, {\"ngram\": \"vengeance\", \"from\": 30736, \"to\": 30745}, {\"ngram\": \"judgment\", \"from\": 30757, \"to\": 30765}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(For you youngsters, there were once four such sins.\", \"from\": 30768, \"to\": 30820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"you youngsters\", \"from\": 30773, \"to\": 30787}, {\"ngram\": \"four such sins\", \"from\": 30805, \"to\": 30819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Look it up.)\", \"from\": 30821, \"to\": 30833, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, that is precisely wha