dealt Mother Church its share of ignominy, but never did they threaten the very cornerstone of her doctrinal patrimony.\", \"from\": 38889, \"to\": 39038, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 38925, \"end\": 38938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mother_church\", \"score\": 0.9999732135956612, \"rank\": 2.678712184914598e-05, \"text\": \"Mother Church\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mother_church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mother_church\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those historical periods\", \"from\": 38894, \"to\": 38918}, {\"ngram\": \"its share\", \"from\": 38939, \"to\": 38948}, {\"ngram\": \"ignominy\", \"from\": 38952, \"to\": 38960}, {\"ngram\": \"the very cornerstone\", \"from\": 38990, \"to\": 39010}, {\"ngram\": \"her doctrinal patrimony\", \"from\": 39014, \"to\": 39037}]}, {\"sentence\": \"None would have mocked the very foundations of the moral law, indeed of the divinely established order of sexual difference.\", \"from\": 39039, \"to\": 39163, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"None\", \"from\": 39039, \"to\": 39043}, {\"ngram\": \"the very foundations\", \"from\": 39062, \"to\": 39082}, {\"ngram\": \"the moral law\", \"from\": 39086, \"to\": 39099}, {\"ngram\": \"the divinely established order\", \"from\": 39111, \"to\": 39141}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual difference\", \"from\": 39145, \"to\": 39162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And if they had, they would have been met by all the ferocity of her thundering condemnations.If the Holy Roman Church were as strong now as it was in the times of the Roman persecutions, the Middle Ages, or in the pontificates of Blessed Pius IX or St. Pius X, would this kind of blasphemy have shown its face?Tweet ThisThose manic forces were kept at bay by the might of the Church.\", \"from\": 39164, \"to\": 39548, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 39270, \"end\": 39275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ancient_Rome\", \"score\": 0.9301791250202353, \"rank\": 0.0749817