us blasphemy\", \"from\": 42762, \"to\": 42786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the absence of howling outrage.\", \"from\": 42788, \"to\": 42826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the absence\", \"from\": 42795, \"to\": 42806}, {\"ngram\": \"outrage\", \"from\": 42818, \"to\": 42825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No such supine reaction would have met such an attack on Islam.\", \"from\": 42827, \"to\": 42890, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No such supine reaction\", \"from\": 42827, \"to\": 42850}, {\"ngram\": \"such an attack\", \"from\": 42866, \"to\": 42880}, {\"ngram\": \"Islam\", \"from\": 42884, \"to\": 42889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For all its wild aberrations, it does not lack the manliness of instantaneous fury.\", \"from\": 42891, \"to\": 42974, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all its wild aberrations\", \"from\": 42895, \"to\": 42919}, {\"ngram\": \"the manliness\", \"from\": 42938, \"to\": 42951}, {\"ngram\": \"instantaneous fury\", \"from\": 42955, \"to\": 42973}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not so the once chest-thumping Catholicism of the saints and martyrs.\", \"from\": 42975, \"to\": 43044, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Not so the once chest-thumping Catholicism\", \"from\": 42975, \"to\": 43017}, {\"ngram\": \"the saints\", \"from\": 43021, \"to\": 43031}, {\"ngram\": \"martyrs\", \"from\": 43036, \"to\": 43043}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sixty years ago, that millennial Catholic trademark was thought embarrassing for a Church in a hurry to make friends with the world.\", \"from\": 43045, \"to\": 43177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 43078, \"end\": 43086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999999988760919, \"rank\": 1.0333251667342252e-09, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a Church\", \"from\": 43126, \"to\": 