n for vengeance\\\": \\\"passing judgment.\\\"\", \"from\": 43479, \"to\": 43703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 43568, \"end\": 43576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999999988760919, \"rank\": 1.0333251667342252e-09, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some members\", \"from\": 43479, \"to\": 43491}, {\"ngram\": \"the hierarchy\", \"from\": 43495, \"to\": 43508}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"proselytism\", \"from\": 43523, \"to\": 43535}, {\"ngram\": \"a slur\", \"from\": 43538, \"to\": 43544}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 43557, \"to\": 43560}, {\"ngram\": \"Catholics\", \"from\": 43584, \"to\": 43593}, {\"ngram\": \"the one and only sin\", \"from\": 43625, \"to\": 43645}, {\"ngram\": \"heaven\", \"from\": 43661, \"to\": 43667}, {\"ngram\": \"vengeance\", \"from\": 43672, \"to\": 43681}, {\"ngram\": \"judgment\", \"from\": 43693, \"to\": 43701}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(For you youngsters, there were once four such sins.\", \"from\": 43704, \"to\": 43756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"you youngsters\", \"from\": 43709, \"to\": 43723}, {\"ngram\": \"four such sins\", \"from\": 43741, \"to\": 43755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Look it up.)\", \"from\": 43757, \"to\": 43769, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, that is precisely what the Decalogue is all about.\", \"from\": 43770, \"to\": 43831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 43808, \"end\": 43817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ten_Commandments\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 6.950345656241069e-13, \"text\": \"Decalogue\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ten_Commandments\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ten_Commandments\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"precisely what\", \"from\": 43789, \"to\": 43803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Exactly the reason why religion classes no longer teach them.\", \"from\": 43832, \"to\": 43893, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Exactly the reason\", \"from\": 43832, \"to\": 43850}, {\"ngram\": \"religion classes\", \"from\": 43855, \"to\": 43871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, some of them do.\", \"from\": 43894, \"to\": 43916, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But you can count them on one hand.This new irenicism-on-steroids is daily reinforced by liturgies eliciting as much fervor and passion for God as the weekly Ladies Auxiliary canasta club.\", \"from\": 43917, \"to\": 44105, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one hand\", \"from\": 43943, \"to\": 43951}, {\"ngram\": \"This new irenicism\", \"from\": 43952, \"to\": 43970}, {\"ngram\": \"steroids\", \"from\": 43974, \"to\": 43982}, {\"ngram\": \"liturgies\", \"from\": 44006, \"to\": 44015}, {\"ngram\": \"as much fervor\", \"from\": 44026, \"to\": 44040}, {\"ngram\": \"passion\", \"from\": 44045, \"to\": 44052}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 44057, \"to\": 44060}, {\"ngram\": \"the weekly Ladies\", \"from\": 44064, \"to\": 44081}, {\"ngram\": \"Auxiliary\", \"from\": 44082, \"to\": 44091}, {\"ngram\": \"canasta\", \"from\": 44092, \"to\": 44099}, {\"ngram\": \"club\", \"from\": 44100, \"to\": 44104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It reminds one of Huxley'sBrave New World's daily doses of the \\\"feelies\\\" to maintain the proper insensate torpor.\", \"from\": 44106, \"to\": 44219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Huxley'sBrave New World's daily doses\", \"from\": 44124, \"to\": 44161}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"feelies\", \"from\": 44165, \"to\": 44177}, {\"ngram\": \"the proper insensate torpor\", \"from\": 44191, \"to\": 44218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This whole dreadful picture is daily propped up by a clergy quite pleased with the standard of a decaying secularity rather than the Standard of Christ the King.\", \"from\": 44220, \"to\": 44381, \"entities\": [], \"