ence\": \"His frightful hordes had decimated much of the former Roman Empire, with its legacy of high civilization and culture.\", \"from\": 53489, \"to\": 53606, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 53543, \"end\": 53555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roman_Empire\", \"score\": 0.9988018247014834, \"rank\": 0.0011949342846063091, \"text\": \"Roman Empire\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roman_Empire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roman_Empire\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His frightful hordes\", \"from\": 53489, \"to\": 53509}, {\"ngram\": \"its legacy\", \"from\": 53562, \"to\": 53572}, {\"ngram\": \"high civilization\", \"from\": 53576, \"to\": 53593}, {\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 53598, \"to\": 53605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now that barbarian was at the very gates of Rome.\", \"from\": 53607, \"to\": 53656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 53651, \"end\": 53655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roman_Empire\", \"score\": 0.778066255660429, \"rank\": 0.2101330835490087, \"text\": \"Rome\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roman_Empire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roman_Empire\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"barbarian\", \"from\": 53616, \"to\": 53625}, {\"ngram\": \"the very gates\", \"from\": 53633, \"to\": 53647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All seemed to be lost.\", \"from\": 53657, \"to\": 53679, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pope Leo the Great, in solemn procession with priests, deacons, and acolytes swinging golden thuribles, went out to meet the bloodthirsty chieftain.\", \"from\": 53680, \"to\": 53828, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Great\", \"from\": 53689, \"to\": 53698}, {\"ngram\": \"solemn procession\", \"from\": 53703, \"to\": 53720}, {\"ngram\": \"priests\", \"from\": 53726, \"to\": 53733}, {\"ngram\": \"deacons\", \"from\": 53735, \"to\": 53742}, {\"ngram\": \"golden thuribles\", \"from\": 53766, \"to\": 53782}, {\"ngram\": \"the bloodthirsty chieftain\", \"from\": 53801, \"to\": 53827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Face-to-face, they spoke.\", \"from\": 53829, \"to\": 53854, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"face\", \"from\": 53837, \"to\": 53841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a brief conversation, Attila turned around and commanded his troops to retreat.\", \"from\": 53855, \"to\": 53940, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 53883, \"end\": 53889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Attila\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.282104240816861e-18, \"text\": \"Attila\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Attila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Attila\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a brief conversation\", \"from\": 53861, \"to\": 53881}, {\"ngram\": \"his troops\", \"from\": 53918, \"to\": 53928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rome was saved.\", \"from\": 53941, \"to\": 53956, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 53941, \"end\": 53945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\", \"score\": 0.5398891901713158, \"rank\": 0.4459112527762948, \"text\": \"Rome\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Christianity was saved.\", \"from\": 53957, \"to\": 53980, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 53957, \"end\": 53969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.8482348503140192, \"rank\": 0.17886606263583446, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Civilization could breathe again.And Leo became known to the ages as \\\"the Great.\", \"from\": 53981, \"to\": 54061, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 54018, \"end\": 54021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Phokas_the_Younger\", \"score\