cession with priests, deacons, and acolytes swinging golden thuribles, went out to meet the bloodthirsty chieftain.\", \"from\": 63253, \"to\": 63401, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Great\", \"from\": 63262, \"to\": 63271}, {\"ngram\": \"solemn procession\", \"from\": 63276, \"to\": 63293}, {\"ngram\": \"priests\", \"from\": 63299, \"to\": 63306}, {\"ngram\": \"deacons\", \"from\": 63308, \"to\": 63315}, {\"ngram\": \"golden thuribles\", \"from\": 63339, \"to\": 63355}, {\"ngram\": \"the bloodthirsty chieftain\", \"from\": 63374, \"to\": 63400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Face-to-face, they spoke.\", \"from\": 63402, \"to\": 63427, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"face\", \"from\": 63410, \"to\": 63414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a brief conversation, Attila turned around and commanded his troops to retreat.\", \"from\": 63428, \"to\": 63513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 63456, \"end\": 63462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Attila\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.194777062409061e-30, \"text\": \"Attila\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Attila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Attila\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a brief conversation\", \"from\": 63434, \"to\": 63454}, {\"ngram\": \"his troops\", \"from\": 63491, \"to\": 63501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rome was saved.\", \"from\": 63514, \"to\": 63529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 63514, \"end\": 63518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roman_Empire\", \"score\": 0.9256361542197126, \"rank\": 0.024521208270728862, \"text\": \"Rome\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roman_Empire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roman_Empire\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Christianity was saved.\", \"from\": 63530, \"to\": 63553, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 63530, \"end\": 63542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.946702