one\", \"from\": 71219, \"to\": 71236}, {\"ngram\": \"Ph.D.\", \"from\": 71238, \"to\": 71243}, {\"ngram\": \"an adjunct professor\", \"from\": 71248, \"to\": 71268}, {\"ngram\": \"philosophy\", \"from\": 71272, \"to\": 71282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His articles have appeared inSt.\", \"from\": 71329, \"to\": 71361, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His articles\", \"from\": 71329, \"to\": 71341}]}, {\"sentence\": \"John's Law Review, The Latin Mass, New Oxford ReviewandThe Journal of Catholic Legal Studies.He can be reached atwww.fatherperricone.com.\", \"from\": 71362, \"to\": 71499, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"John's Law Review\", \"from\": 71362, \"to\": 71379}, {\"ngram\": \"The Latin Mass\", \"from\": 71381, \"to\": 71395}, {\"ngram\": \"New Oxford ReviewandThe Journal\", \"from\": 71397, \"to\": 71428}, {\"ngram\": \"Catholic Legal Studies\", \"from\": 71432, \"to\": 71454}, {\"ngram\": \"atwww.fatherperricone.com\", \"from\": 71473, \"to\": 71498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Blasphemy on such a grand scale as the Opening Ceremonies of the Paris Olympics would have been unthinkable.\", \"from\": 71501, \"to\": 71609, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Blasphemy\", \"from\": 71501, \"to\": 71510}, {\"ngram\": \"such a grand scale\", \"from\": 71514, \"to\": 71532}, {\"ngram\": \"the Opening Ceremonies\", \"from\": 71536, \"to\": 71558}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 71562, \"to\": 71580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, Napolean kidnapped Pope Pius VII in 1809, dragging him across the Alps in precarious health to Fontainebleau.\", \"from\": 71610, \"to\": 71724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 71710, \"end\": 71723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fontainebleau\", \"score\": 0.9999269089770244, \"rank\": 7.309604202431553e-05, \"text\": \"Fontainebleau\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fontainebleau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fontainebleau\"}], \"nou